      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 max-w-3xl mb-8">
        Same-day appointments often available. Call 754-215-2272.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#4da3ff] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold hover:bg-[#3d8fe0] transition-colors sm:w-64">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
