          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
          </svg>
          Call 754-215-2272
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Content Capsules -->
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-12">

      <!-- What Does Auto Upholstery Cleaning Include -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">What Does Auto Upholstery Cleaning Include?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong>Auto upholstery cleaning includes deep extraction of fabric seats, carpet shampooing, leather cleaning, and stain removal from all soft surfaces inside your vehicle. In Fort Lauderdale, we also treat for mildew and moisture trapped in upholstery fibers by Florida's year-round humidity.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Our vehicle upholstery cleaning process starts with thorough vacuuming to remove loose debris, sand, and pet hair. We then apply surface-specific cleaning agents — oxygen-infused shampoo for fabric, pH-balanced cleaner for leather — and use hot water extraction to pull contaminants from deep within the fibers. The result is upholstery that looks, feels, and smells like new.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          For a complete interior restoration, see our <a href={`${base}interior-car-detailing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">interior car detailing service</a> which includes upholstery cleaning plus dashboard, console, and full cabin treatment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Cost -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Much Does Vehicle Upholstery Cleaning Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
