        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong>Mobile auto upholstery cleaning delivers the same results as shop service because we bring professional-grade hot water extractors, steam cleaners, and Chemical Guys products directly to your location. The equipment and technique are identical — the only difference is we come to you in Fort Lauderdale, saving you the trip and wait time.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Our mobile setup includes commercial extraction units, steam cleaning equipment, and a full range of surface-specific products. We carry everything needed for fabric, leather, vinyl, and carpet cleaning. You get shop-quality upholstery cleaning at your home, office, or anywhere in Fort Lauderdale, Dania Beach, Hollywood, and Pompano Beach.
        </p>
