          </p>
          <a href={`${base}leather-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-medium hover:text-[#c0c7cf] transition-colors">
            Learn more about Leather Cleaning Fort Lauderdale →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Leather Conditioning -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-2">Leather Conditioning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
            Professional leather conditioning replenishes essential oils and creates a protective barrier against Florida's UV rays and heat cycling. Prevents cracking, fading, and premature aging of leather upholstery.
