        <a href="https://www.koch-chemie.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-medium hover:text-[#c0c7cf] transition-colors">Koch-Chemie</a> ·
        <a href="https://www.the-ida.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-medium hover:text-[#c0c7cf] transition-colors">International Detailing Association (IDA)</a>
